      • lookup

        List<EntityModifier<?>> lookup(org.bukkit.entity.EntityType type)
        Look up all of the possible modifiers for the given entity type.
        Use lookup(EntityType, Class) if you know the type; it returns a parameterized object instead of a generic.
        Parameters:
        type - the type to search for
        Returns:
        a list containing all of the possible modifiers, ordered by index
